{
  "id": "adv_card_aoi_09_01",
  "title": "井川葵 1話 歌とダンスで生きていく",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "――ふぅ、今日のライブどうだった？\n僕としては、いい感じだったと思うんだけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Whew‚ how was today's live performance?\nI think it went pretty well.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 7.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様。いつも通り良かったよ\n最近仕事が増えたから少し心配だったけど、さすがだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good work. It was good as always.\nI was a bit worried you've had more work lately‚ but as expected of you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "BIG4になっちゃったからね\n仕事が多くなるのは分かってたよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's because I became BIG4.\nI knew I’d be getting more work‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 19.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "その上でコンディションを作ってるんだ\nこころや愛にも、その辺は注意するように言ってある",
      "translations": {
        "en": "so I've been managing my condition with that in mind.\nI've told Kokoro and Ai to be careful about that too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 25.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "だから心配はいらないよ、{user}君",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So there's no need to worry‚ {user}-kun.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "葵は本当にしっかりしているな……\n俺が高校生だった頃とは大違いだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Aoi‚ you're really reliable…\nIt's completely different from when I was in high school.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 35.9333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01-aoi005.m4a",
      "text": "そうかな？　自分ではよく分からないな\nそれに莉央からは仕事ばっかりするな、とか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Really? I’m not so sure myself.\nRio's always telling me not to just work all the time—",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01-aoi006.m4a",
      "text": "学校の友達と遊んだり、学生にしか出来ないことを\n経験しろってよく言われてるけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "to hang out with school friends and experience things\nonly students can.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 49.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01-aoi007.m4a",
      "text": "今はこうして仕事をしてる方が楽しいんだ\nそれに、学校生活にあんまり興味ないしね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But right now‚ working like this is more fun.\nBesides‚ I'm not really interested in school life.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.9941873178,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "興味ないって……学校楽しくないのか？\nもしかして、友達とうまくいってないとか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Not interested…? Is school not fun for you?\nCould it be that you're not getting along with friends…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 64.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01-aoi008.m4a",
      "text": "そんなことないよ。それに、学校に行ってる時は\nちゃんと遊んでるから、心配しなくて大丈夫",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's not it. And I do hang out\nwhen I’m at school‚ so don't worry.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.1383335907,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "なら良かったよ。どんなことをして遊んでるんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's good then. What do you do when you hang out?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 75.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01-aoi009.m4a",
      "text": "男子とフットサルとか、最近はバスケもするかな\nスリーポイントが決まると気持ちいいんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Futsal with the guys‚ and lately basketball too.\nIt feels great when I make a three-pointer.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 82.6333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "毎日レッスンしてるのに学校でも体を動かしてるのか\nそれに、男子に混じってスポーツなんて、葵らしいな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even though you have lessons every day‚ you still exercise at school?\nAnd playing sports with the boys is so like you‚ Aoi.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 91.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01-aoi010.m4a",
      "text": "スポーツしてるのは、男子が多いから\n自然にそうなっちゃうんだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's because there are more boys playing sports‚\nso it naturally ends up that way.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "そうか。葵の体力は並じゃないからな\nその、同性の友達とは……遊んだりしないのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see. Your stamina isn't ordinary‚ Aoi.\nUm‚ what about friends of the same gender? Don't you hang out with them?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 106.4666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01-aoi011.m4a",
      "text": "女子ともそこそこ仲良くはしてるつもりだよ\nバレンタインだって、一杯チョコをもらうし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think I get along reasonably well with the girls too.\nI get lots of chocolate on Valentine's Day‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01-aoi012.m4a",
      "text": "おかげで毎年お返しが大変なんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "so returning the favor is tough every year.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.7333302815,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 115.7999969482
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "葵……バレンタインの意味、知ってるか？\nそれは仲がいいというより……いや、まぁいいか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Aoi… do you know what Valentine's Day means?\nThat's more than just being friends… well‚ never mind.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.0271055779,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "男子とも女子ともうまくやってるなら何よりだ。芸能\n活動をしてる子はたまにクラスで浮いてたりするから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you're getting along well with both boys and girls‚ that's great.\nKids in entertainment sometimes feel out of place in class.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.1365874726,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 132.7999969482
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01-aoi013.m4a",
      "text": "僕に限ってはその心配はいらないかな\n学校でも何も問題はないよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In my case‚ you don't need to worry about that.\nThere are no problems at school either.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.7002545967,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 139.0999969482
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01-aoi014.m4a",
      "text": "だから、もっと沢山仕事を振ってよ\n今、凄く仕事が楽しいんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So give me more work.\nWork is really fun right now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.9333302815,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "そう言ってもらえると俺も嬉しいよ\nなら、俺も頑張ってる葵の仕事をどんどん取ってこよう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It makes me happy to hear you say that.\nThen I'll keep getting more work for you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.7333302815,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 151.9999969482
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01-aoi015.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、僕は今、絶好調だからね\nよろしく頼むよ、{user}君",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ I'm in perfect condition right now.\nPlease take care of it‚ {user}-kun.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 155.6666636149,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "本当に頼もしいな、葵は",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're really dependable‚ Aoi.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 158.8999969482,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
