    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 168.6933353702
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01-aoi016.m4a",
      "text": "どうしたの、{user}君\n至急、話したいことって何？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What's wrong‚ {user}-kun?\nWhat did you urgently want to talk about?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 171.4666636149,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "…………えっと、まぁ、とにかく座って下さい\n葵さん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "………Um‚ well‚ please sit down first.\nAoi-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 179.1407582084,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01-aoi017.m4a",
      "text": "どうして丁寧語なの？　気味が悪いよ\n元気もないし。夏風邪でも引いちゃった？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why are you speaking formally? It's creepy.\nYou seem down too. Did you catch a summer cold?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 184.3666636149,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "元気がないのは、昨日の夜\n葵のご両親から電話をもらったからだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm down because last night\nI got a phone call from your parents‚ Aoi.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 189.3666636149,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01-aoi018.m4a",
      "text": "僕の親から？　なんだろう？\nそういえば、お中元の季節だっけ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "From my parents? What about?\nCome to think of it‚ is it mid-year gift season?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 195.4333302815,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "……違う。葵、学校の出席日数ヤバいらしいな\nこのままだと留年だって聞いたんだけど……本当か？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…No. Aoi‚ apparently your school attendance is bad.\nI heard you'll have to repeat a year at this rate… is that true?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 204.7518634684,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01-aoi019.m4a",
      "text": "そうなの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is that so?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 209.3666707356,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "いやいや、俺が聞いてるんだよ。なんで葵が質問する？\n学校から何か連絡があっただろ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No no‚ I'm the one asking. Why are you asking a question?\nThe school must have contacted you…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 214.5333302815,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01-aoi020.m4a",
      "text": "う～ん、あったかもしれないけど、フットサルの後で\n疲れてたから……あ、そうだ、課題をもらってたっけ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm‚ maybe there was‚ but I was tired after futsal…\nOh‚ right‚ I remember I got some assignments.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 221.1666636149,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01-aoi021.m4a",
      "text": "出席日数が足りない分は普段の宿題にプラスして\n課題を出すから、それをやれって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "To make up for my lack of attendance‚ they told me to do\nextra assignments on top of my usual homework.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 231.3333302815,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01-aoi022.m4a",
      "text": "それを提出すれば、留年は回避出来るらしいよ。多分",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If I submit them‚ I can apparently avoid repeating a year. Probably.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 234.0666676838,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01-koh016.m4a",
      "text": "どうして他人事っぽいリアクションなんだ……\nだったら、絶対やらないとダメじゃないか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why are you reacting like it's someone else's problem…\nThen you absolutely have to do it‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 242.1666636149,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01-aoi023.m4a",
      "text": "そうだね。でも、まだ全然手をつけてないんだ\n宿題も課題も",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's right. But I haven't started on it at all yet.\nNeither homework nor assignments.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 248.8999969482,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01-koh017.m4a",
      "text": "……昨日は、何も問題ないって言ってたよな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Yesterday you said there were no problems‚ didn't you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 250.5000010172,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01-aoi024.m4a",
      "text": "問題はないよ。仕事に支障はきたさないから\n安心して",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There's no problem. It won't interfere with work‚\nso don't worry.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 257.2666605631,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01-aoi025.m4a",
      "text": "だから、もっと沢山仕事を振ってよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So give me more work.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 258.6000010172,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01-koh018.m4a",
      "text": "今のスケジュールで、宿題と課題を両方こなすなんて\n……無理だ。仕事を増やすどころか、減らさないと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "With your current schedule‚ handling both homework and assignments\nis impossible… Far from increasing work‚ we need to reduce it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 265.4333302815,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01-aoi026.m4a",
      "text": "それは嫌だよ。一度引き受けた仕事を断るなんて\n先方に迷惑が掛かるじゃないか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don't want that. Turning down work I've already accepted\nwould cause trouble for the other party.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 274.3666636149,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01-koh019.m4a",
      "text": "だからって、葵を留年させるわけにはいかない\nそんなことになったら、ご両親に顔向け出来ないよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But even so‚ I can't let you repeat a year‚ Aoi.\nIf that happened‚ I couldn't face your parents.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 280.1333302815,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01-aoi027.m4a",
      "text": "うん、それで考えたんだけどね\n君に聞いてほしいんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ so I've been thinking about it.\nI want you to listen.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 287.2999969482,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01-aoi028.m4a",
      "text": "僕は歌とダンスで生きていく\nこれはもう決めたことだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm going to live through song and dance.\nI've already decided this.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 292.1666839599,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01-aoi029.m4a",
      "text": "だから、中途半端なことはもうやめよう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So let's stop doing things halfway.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 294.1666880289,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01-koh020.m4a",
      "text": "おい、それってつまり……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ that means…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 297.9666880289,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_09_01-aoi030.m4a",
      "text": "うん。僕、学校辞めようと思うんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. I'm thinking of quitting school.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 300.7000213622,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
